&#13;The 26-year-old was working in a shed at the back of his property in the suburb of Kaiti earlier this afternoon.</p>&#13;<p>
&#13;He suffered burns to his right leg and arm.</p>&#13;<p>
&#13;The Fire Service says the cigarette lit a shade cloth and a couch in the shed.</p>&#13;<p>
&#13;They say it shows just how important it is to take care when lighting cigarettes around flammable liquids.</p>&#13;<p>- <a href="http://www.newstalkzb.co.nz" target="_blank">Newstalk ZB</a></p> 	&#13;</div>&#13;&#13;&#13;</div></body></html>
